room_title: Escape room "All In" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
room_description: It was all a setup. The dealer was in on it, the other high rollers at the table and even the waitress played her part. They took you for everything you had. Unfortunately for them, you have a plan to take it back... with interest. You call up a few "business associates" and explain the job. They all think you're certifiably insane... and they all want in.
